HEADWORD: Cross-tail
<hw>Cross"-tail`</hw> <pr>(-t?l`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Steam
Engine)</fld> <def>A bar connecting the ends of the side rods or levers
of a backaction or side-lever engine.</def>⟦br⟧
